    old "But no guards to be seen."
    new "But no guards to be seen."

    old "Her exhaustion caught up to her, breathing heavy, panting."
    new "Her exhaustion caught up to her, breathing heavy, panting."

    old "She could feel the sweat that had been building on her body."
    new "She could feel the sweat that had been building on her body."

    old "Her hair a mess, clinging to her neck."
    new "Her hair a mess, clinging to her neck."

