    new "I don't know. Maybe..."

    old "Maybe we fucked with a merchant that had more connections than I figured."
    new "Maybe we fucked with a merchant that had more connections than I figured."

    old "Whatever the reason, we're too hot right now."
    new "Whatever the reason, we're too hot right now."

    old "We gotta lay low for a bit."
    new "We gotta lay low for a bit."

    old "Sarah nodded. It seemed the safest choice."
    new "Sarah nodded. It seemed the safest choice."

    old "Gods, how had she ended up here? How quickly had her life turned about..."
    new "Gods, how had she ended up here? How quickly had her life turned about..."

