    new "Alaric punched the wall."

    old "We gotta get off the streets, let the heat die down."
    new "We gotta get off the streets, let the heat die down."

    old "He looked at her with angry eyes."
    new "He looked at her with angry eyes."

    old "This is your fault, you know that?"
    new "This is your fault, you know that?"

