    old "Alaric looked around."
    new "Alaric looked around."

    old "Okay...think..."
    new "Okay...think..."

    old "Sarah could see him racking his brain."
    new "Sarah could see him racking his brain."

    old "She wished she could help him, but the truth was, she hardly knew this city at all."
    new "She wished she could help him, but the truth was, she hardly knew this city at all."

    old "She had no idea where it would be safe or not."
    new "She had no idea where it would be safe or not."

    old "We can..."
    new "We can..."

    old "Fuck...not ideal, but we could..."
    new "Fuck...not ideal, but we could..."

    old "His voice trailed off."
    new "His voice trailed off."

