    new "Yeah. I got a few friends there...they might be able to put us up."

    old "Okay...is it far?"
    new "Okay...is it far?"

    old "Alaric shook his head."
    new "Alaric shook his head."

    old "We can make it, sticking to the alleys."
    new "We can make it, sticking to the alleys."

    old "But best we travel by night."
    new "But best we travel by night."

    old "Sarah nodded. She couldn't do much else but agree with him. They were in this together now."
    new "Sarah nodded. She couldn't do much else but agree with him. They were in this together now."

    old "The two of them sat about in the alley, waiting for the hours to pass."
    new "The two of them sat about in the alley, waiting for the hours to pass."

    old "Tearing up some fabrics from a nearby crate, Alaric made two cloaks for them to hide their appearance."
    new "Tearing up some fabrics from a nearby crate, Alaric made two cloaks for them to hide their appearance."

    old "When the sun had finally set, the two of them set out."
    new "When the sun had finally set, the two of them set out."

    old "Sticking close to Alaric, Sarah made her way through the city."
    new "Sticking close to Alaric, Sarah made her way through the city."

    old "As per usual, it seemed like Alaric knew the alleys of Lethram like the back of his hand."
    new "As per usual, it seemed like Alaric knew the alleys of Lethram like the back of his hand."

    old "Twisting and turning, they dissapeared into the back streets of Lethram."
    new "Twisting and turning, they dissapeared into the back streets of Lethram."

