    new "Sarah saw the night life of the city."

    old "How just as the legal part of the city fell asleep, the illegal part came to life."
    new "How just as the legal part of the city fell asleep, the illegal part came to life."

    old "Gambling houses, drug dens and all manner of criminal enterprise rose up."
