    new "Yeah. Let's keep going."

    old "As they turned down one of the alleys, a large stone stairway appeared."
    new "As they turned down one of the alleys, a large stone stairway appeared."

    old "It ran along the length of a sewer canal."
    new "It ran along the length of a sewer canal."

