    old "People didn't seem to care here."
    new "People didn't seem to care here."

    old "And above all, not a guard in sight."
    new "And above all, not a guard in sight."

    old "After hours of walking, Alaric finally slowed down."
    new "After hours of walking, Alaric finally slowed down."

    old "He turned to her."
    new "He turned to her."

    old "Sarah nodded again."
    new "Sarah nodded again."

    old "Good. Because we're here."
    new "Good. Because we're here."

    old "Sarah looked around."
    new "Sarah looked around."

    old "Here?"
    new "Here?"

