    old "This...is The Den."
    new "This...is The Den."

    old "Sarah could feel the emphasis he placed on the name."
    new "Sarah could feel the emphasis he placed on the name."

    old "For a man that never seemed to take much serious, even he seemed afraid."
    new "For a man that never seemed to take much serious, even he seemed afraid."

    old "What's...The Den?"
    new "What's...The Den?"

