    old "But there were plenty of deaths on both sides. And near the end, even the City Guard wanted to end the conflict."
    new "But there were plenty of deaths on both sides. And near the end, even the City Guard wanted to end the conflict."

    old "So they struck a deal."
    new "So they struck a deal."

    old "A deal?"
    new "A deal?"

    old "Yeah, with the first Underboss."
    new "Yeah, with the first Underboss."

    old "He was a fella that had enough muscle and rep to hold down all the other gangs."
    new "He was a fella that had enough muscle and rep to hold down all the other gangs."

    old "And he said if the City Guard let him keep his blocks and pulled out, the war would be over."
    new "And he said if the City Guard let him keep his blocks and pulled out, the war would be over."

    old "The City Guard agreed."
    new "The City Guard agreed."

    old "In the years after, East Lethram recovered, but instead of housing blocks, we got sprawling slums."
    new "In the years after, East Lethram recovered, but instead of housing blocks, we got sprawling slums."

    old "Worse to live in, but easier to police."
    new "Worse to live in, but easier to police."

    old "All except for one part of town."
    new "All except for one part of town."

    old "Alaric gestured at the door."
    new "Alaric gestured at the door."

    old "That there is the last housing block that is still standing."
    new "That there is the last housing block that is still standing."

    old "A practical fortress in the heart of East Lethram."
    new "A practical fortress in the heart of East Lethram."

    old "The Den."
    new "The Den."

    old "It's one way in and one way out."
    new "It's one way in and one way out."

    old "And it's still ruled over by the Underboss."
    new "And it's still ruled over by the Underboss."

    old "Not the same guy as all those years ago, but same title."
    new "Not the same guy as all those years ago, but same title."

    old "This here is pretty much the Palace of Crime in Lethram."
    new "This here is pretty much the Palace of Crime in Lethram."

    old "Sarah felt a building dread in her chest."
    new "Sarah felt a building dread in her chest."

    old "Why...are you telling me all of this?"
    new "Why...are you telling me all of this?"

    old "Because when we step in there, I'll do what I can, but even I can't control what happens in there."
    new "Because when we step in there, I'll do what I can, but even I can't control what happens in there."

    old "There are people in there...dangerous people..."
